<plot>Kylie Harrison has a problem; her husband Mark just won't stay dead. At the end of her rope she calls in some experts, Chance and Ben of Aubrey/Bennett Investigations to deal with her supernatural problems. From the outset, the bickering paranormalists talk a good game, but it quickly becomes clear they may be out of their depth. Things take a turn for the surreal when Mark, alive and well, returns home from work to find his wife and a pair of ghost hunters creeping around a dark house. Is the house really haunted? Is Mark really dead? Do Chance and Ben have any idea what they are doing?</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?581389</url></doc>
